Description: Multiverse analyses run the same (or very similar) analyses over a
    range of arbitrary data processing decisions. We provide an intervace for creating
    analysis decision grids and generating all possible combinations of those decisions. 
    Grids can be lists of data filtering criteria, different versions of IVs and DVs, 
    and/or modeling strategies.
